With dbus:
qmake CONFIG-=sse2 CONFIG+=no-asio CONFIG+=no-g15 CONFIG+=no-11x CONFIG+=no-bonjour CONFIG+=no-server CONFIG+=no-elevation CONFIG+=no-update -recursive

Without dbus (recommended, mandatory for use with Imprudence on Windows):
qmake CONFIG-=sse2 CONFIG+=no-asio CONFIG+=no-g15 CONFIG+=no-11x CONFIG+=no-bonjour CONFIG+=no-server CONFIG+=no-dbus CONFIG+=no-elevation CONFIG+=no-update -recursive

On Linux you might want to add CONFIG+=bundled-speex CONFIG+=bundled-celt
For Debian/Ubuntu/based Linux distros you might need to use qmake-qt4 instead of qmake

Windows:
nmake release

Linux:
make
